There is an extra greater-than symbol in the FAQ->Background documentation,
which turns up next to the question 'May I use the Apache logo on my product or
Web site?'. 

Affected page is:

http://httpd.apache.org/docs/2.2/faq/background.html

Search for 'background.logo' in the source to find it.
